articles.title: M Emmet Walsh: Knives Out director pays tribute to acting 'legend' - BBC.com
articles.description: M Emmet Walsh, who has died at the age of 88, was one of Hollywood's most admired character actors.

articles.title: ‘Peaky Blinders’ Movie A Go With Cillian Murphy Returning, Production To Kick Off In September, Creator Steven Knight Says - Deadline
articles.description: The long-teased 'Peaky Blinders' movie is officially ago, with Cillian Murphy returning and production starting in September, per the show's creator.
